    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "a metallic corrugated ball, slightly larger than a baseball,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "with a wire attached to it. The writer asked Mr. [REDACTED] what",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "he thought the object was, and he replied, \"not being a geologist",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "he could not say\". Mr. [REDACTED] was asked if he thought",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "the object was a bomb, and he replied that he did not know,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "but it hadn't blown up yet.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "The writer referred Mr. [REDACTED] to the Oklahoma City Police",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
